data.caption: This beautiful woman is too humble to post many pictures of herself. Thank you Chante for being such a wonderful mother and wife. Thank you for being courageous enough to deliver our two wonderful children in spite if it all. You make me gladly look forward to each day, month and year together.
A very rare sighting of Elliot sitting still. Old 97's performing "Good with God" captured his attention.
It turns out that a dog's loyalty can be bought.
